ZZZ's models are found in a number of different mods being used for various things, since he gave open permission for anyone who wants to use them to do so. (and they're amazing, so people want to find uses for them.)

They're a bit unusual in that regard.  They show up in a lot of places.

Hm. I'd guess, judging by the varying colors and sizes of the containers as well as their position on that ridiculously large ship, that it's from some kind of life support mod. (or being used for that purpose, anyway.) I don't see them being used for anything in the video.
